metadata.name: Earth goddess #1
metadata.description:
The CUBE represents earth and life
Green, alive and fresh
The earth goddess is fresh in it

Dead SOIL represents the outside of the earth and the space around it

And the dead TREES that completely surround our planet are a sign of toxic outer space


The cube represents earth and life

Dead soil represents the outside of the earth and the space around it

Everything is handmade
We brought a tree
We created a glass cube
We brought soil
No AI or special editing is used in it
